ygData.messageBody:
You can find the holo of light sple in queynos. At the clercir /druid or
paladin guild don t remember :)
To all wizzard, buy this spel ! He is really incredible ! More light then a
greater lightstone AND a headband with .. ac 3... Cool to replace your cloth
armor (in fact you get +2 in ac when you use it). I am now a 202 at ac with
an erudin wizzard (and with only the base point in agility and dex). TANK
WIZZARD RULES ! :)


see you


yakos

level 13 wizzard
